        <briefdescription>
<para>Initialize a specific watchdog timer instance/driver. </para>        </briefdescription>
        <detaileddescription>
<para>This function must be called before other functions of the driver are called.</para><para><parameterlist kind="param"><parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
<parametername>InstancePtr</parametername>
</parameternamelist>
<parameterdescription>
<para>is a pointer to the <ref refid="struct_x_scu_wdt" kindref="compound">XScuWdt</ref> instance. </para></parameterdescription>
</parameteritem>
<parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
<parametername>ConfigPtr</parametername>
</parameternamelist>
<parameterdescription>
<para>is the config structure. </para></parameterdescription>
</parameteritem>
<parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
<parametername>EffectiveAddress</parametername>
</parameternamelist>
<parameterdescription>
<para>is the base address for the device. It could be a virtual address if address translation is supported in the system, otherwise it is the physical address.</para></parameterdescription>
</parameteritem>
</parameterlist>
<simplesect kind="return"><para><itemizedlist>
<listitem><para>XST_SUCCESS if initialization was successful.</para></listitem><listitem><para>XST_DEVICE_IS_STARTED if the device has already been started.</para></listitem></itemizedlist>
</para></simplesect>
<simplesect kind="note"><para>This function enables the watchdog mode. </para></simplesect>
</para>        </detaileddescription>
